IN RE the Personal Restraint of Steven Loren HESSELGRAVE, Petitioner. No. 95189-6 Supreme Court of Washington. DATED at Olympia, Washington, September 6, 2018.

ORDER

¶ 1 This matter came before the Court on its September 6, 2018, En Banc Conference. The Court considered the motion and the files herein. A majority of the Court voted in favor of the following result:

¶ 2 Now, therefore, it is hereby

¶ 3 ORDERED:

¶ 4 That the motion for discretionary review is denied.

For the Court

/s/ Fairhurst, C.J. CHIEF JUSTICE
